This is for rebuilding lighting with Lightmass. Everything inside will get the full quality indirect bounce light. It also creates the samples for dynamic objects. Dynamic objects outside of the volume will not have indirect lighting. Static geometry outside of the volume will have only 1 indirect bounce of light.
